item.title: Data describing habitat use and availability for wild waterfowl in California, USA
item.description: Abstract These data describe the overlap of wild waterfowl and domestic poultry operations in California, USA. These data support a paired USGS publication. Access Points https://www.sciencebase.gov/catalog/item/65537ff0d34ee4b6e05c3d64
